                     Chimera 2.0 Overview 
                

  Chimera's architecture . Chimera employs a distributed architecture divided between a user's computing environment and Chimera-enhanced websites. 

  Hypermedia concepts . Chimera has an underlying set of hypermedia concepts that enable hypermedia services in a wide range of client applications. 

  Related papers . A diverse set of papers have been written about Chimera. They are accessible in a variety of formats. 

      
